``.data``          -          View Your Data in GB

``.presets``          -          See available Website Presets

``.countries``          -          See the list of countries available

``.generate``          -          Generates a proxy list

**STICKY**
``.generate sticky de 1000`` - Generates 1000 sticky german proxies
``.generate sticky us 1000`` - Generates 1000 sticky us proxies
``.generate sticky ftl 1000`` - Generates 1000 sticky footlockereu proxies

**ROTATING**
      ``.generate rotating de 1000`` - Generates 1000 rotating german proxies
      ``.generate rotating us 1000`` - Generates 1000 rotating usa proxies
``.generate rotating ftl 1000`` - Generates 1000 rotating footlocker EU proxies
